<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>디미고인</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #151515;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    }
    .center-section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .login-btn {
      background: #232325;
      color: #fff;
      width: 270px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: none;
      margin: 24px 0 8px 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .login-btn svg {
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .forgot-link {
      color: #6e6e6e;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      text-decoration: underline;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .scenery {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 450px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="center-section">
    <div style="margin-bottom:32px;">
      <img src="logo.svg" alt="디미고인 로고" width="56" />
    </div>
    <div style="color:#fff;font-size:22px;font-weight:600; margin-bottom:36px;">디미고인</div>
    <button class="login-btn">
      <img src="/google.svg" alt="Google Logo" width="24" height="24" />
      디미고 구글 계정으로 로그인
    </button>
    <div class="forgot-link">인증번호를 잊으셨나요?</div>
  </div>
  <!-- Scenery SVG at the bottom -->
  <div class="scenery">
    <img src="scenery.svg" alt="Scenery" style="width:100%;" />
  </div>
</body>
</html>
